Ronald Adam (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ronald_Adam_(actor) 0 Ronald George Hinings Adams OBE (31 December 1896 – 28 March 1979), known professionally as Ronald Adam, was a British officer of the RFC and RAF, an actor on stage and screen, and a successful theatre manager.
